data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom home on .40 of an acre with Newer AC (2021) AND Roof (2017). The split floor plan is perfect for gatherings as well as quiet time for work, school or R & R. It's the best of both worlds! The layout includes 3 bedrooms, a generously sized great room, kitchen with stainless steel appliance package and two full baths! Just out back is a covered lanai overlooking your very own HUGE private fenced yard. Have endless fun grilling, enjoying Florida's sunny days, or whatever your heart desires! There is also plenty of room to build a pool and loads of space for storage if needed for toys, trailers, boats etc. An additional upgrade includes the renovated shower in the primary suite bathroom.  The location is second to none! Only a short drive from world class attractions including Walt Disney World Resort, Posner park, dining, shopping, medical facilities and major highways (including US HWY 27 and I-4), making your commute to anywhere in Central Florida a breeze! Schedule your private tour today!
